WEBVTT

01:05:00.983 --> 01:05:02.441
We should set some kind of trap.

01:05:03.858 --> 01:05:05.941
The ones who come to steal
these plantains

01:05:05.941 --> 01:05:07.191
are just poor petty thieves.

01:05:07.774 --> 01:05:09.191
They're probably just hungry.

01:05:10.858 --> 01:05:12.608
I don't think they're so poor.
